# Aura Manim (ch 6+)

Read `Aura/design-video/AGENTS.md` and `Aura/design-video/MANIM-STANDARDS.md` before editing scenes or components.

## Mandatory before user handoff

1. `manim -ql` render changed acts
2. `python Aura/design-video/tools/extract_act_frames.py --scene sceneN_actM`
3. Vision-check PNGs against MANIM-STANDARDS frame checklist
4. Fix and re-render until pass

## Code

- Readable copy: `typography.body_text()` / `caption_line()` — not raw `Text`
- Diagrams: `components.layout.flow_lr` + `fit_center`; arrows after layout
- Never scale groups containing readable `Text`
- New chapter visuals: compose primitives; no private `_foo_text()` helpers
- `vo/sceneN.md` PLAY CHECKLIST + VO seed at act creation

## Frozen

Do not refactor `scene0`–`scene5` act files or their chapter components (`segmentation`, `texture_bake`).

## Pacing

Default `scene.wait(5.5)`; user bulk-adjusts via `tools/adjust_waits.py` after read-aloud.
